summary: Merry Christmas! 🎄🎉⛄
body:
Merry Christmas! 🎄🎉⛄

(I’m from Australia so Christmas is in the summer and it’s a dayish earlier than most countries)

Remember to control your portions and control the types of food you eat✨

If you over eat a little bit, dance those extra calories away to your favorite Christmas songs and remember to drink lots of water to keep you feeling full and your skin clear ❄️
